# Original Idea

Per-room/thread skills: load skills from a room/thread session's effective_cwd workspace subfolder (.claude/skills, .claude-p/skills), merged with global+builtin skills. Follow-up to B706 (which delivered per-room AGENTS.md/CLAUDE.md project-doc autoload from effective_cwd). Requires threading effective_cwd through Skills.available_skills/expand_skill_refs/available_skills_as_tools and their call sites (session_turn, prompt_builder), plus per-room scan/cache merged with the global atomic cache. Larger/riskier than the docs change; deliberately deferred from B706.

